Package org.jscripter.emu.java.lang Description

Re-compilation helping classes for emulation of java.lang package.

These classes and interfaces are not for JS applications but only used internally by JS re-complier implementations for emulation.

Please refer to the Java API Standards for detail description of the original java.lang.* classes and interfaces.
